quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  57,16,"E yontaani gom…óim…ďe …ďen nde …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen dee∆īirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ďe wa'aali wa …ďen okkanoo…ďe Defte …ďen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ďen, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yoori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ď…ďe kon ko faasiqii…ďe"
  57,17,"Anndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay leydi ndin …ďaawo ndi yoorii. Gom…óii Men …ďannginiranii on Aayeeje …óen, fii no haqqiliron"
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ďe (jawle mun …ďen) ka wor…ďe e ka rew…ďe …ďe √Īawli Allah √Īamaande labaande, …ďe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi"
  57,19,"∆Āen gom…óim…ďe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, ko …ďen woni goongiyaŇčke en. Sahodin…ďe …ďen ka Joomi mun, hino woodani …ďen njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe e annoora ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āen non yeddu…ďe …ďe fenni Aayeeje Amen …óen, ko …ďen woni yim…ďe Jahiimi ngen"
  57,20,"Anndee wonnde nguurndam aduna …óam ko fijindaaru, e mbelee…óe, e cu…óaari, e …ďurondiro hakkunde mon e jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe. Wano to…ďo haawnungo remoo…ďe …ďen pu…ói mun, refti ngo yoora, yi'aa hingo soy…ói; refti ngo wonta muncii…óum. Hino ka laakara, lette sa…ótu…óe, e yaafuyee immorde e Allah e yarluyee. Nguurndam aduna …óam wonaali, si wanaa dakammehoy hodo"
  57,21,"Adondiree e (golle) yaafaawuya ka Joomi mon, e Aljanna mo yaajeendi mun wa'i yaajeendi kammu ngun e leydi ndin, on maranaama …ďen gom…óim…ďe Allah e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen. ∆äum ko …ďural Allah ngal O okkata on mo O muuyani. Allah ko Jom …ďural mawnungal"
  57,22,"Bone woo he…ďataa [on] e leydi ndin maa e pittaali mon …óin, si wanaa …óum woniino e deftere ado Men tagude ndee [tagoore]. Pellet, …óum ko ko newanii Allah"
  57,23,"Ko fii wata on suno e ko laawii on kon, wanaa kadi weltorgol ko O okki on kon. Allah yi…óaa kala √Īaa∆īoowo, mantii…óo"
  57,24,"∆Āen wuddoo…ďe …ďe yamira yim…ďe …ďen nguddam... kala …óuurnii…óo, pellet, Allah kan ko Galo, Yettinii…óo"
  57,25,"Gom…óii Men nulirii Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen …ďanngannduyeeji, Men jippindinani …ďe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ďe …ďen √Īii…ďira e nun…óal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mun e nafooje wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, e no Allah fe√Ī√Īinira …ďen walloo…ďe Mo e Nulaa…óo Makko on ka wirnii. Pellet, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Foolu…óo. @Corrected"
  57,26,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima, Men wa…ói e geyngol ma…ď…ďe ngol Annabaaku e Defte. Hino e ma…ď…ďe feewu…ďe, ko …óuu…ói kon e ma…ď…ďe ko faasiqii…ďe"
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkindini e batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin, Nulaa…ďe Amen [goo], Men jokkintiniri […ďe] Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men wa…ói e …ďer…óe jokku…ďe mo …ďen : yurmeende e giggol. Labbeyaagal ngal …ďe sinci ngal, Menen Men wa…ó…óinaa ngal e ma…ď…ďe. [Men lamndaaki] si wanaa …óa…ď…ďugol welayee Allah. Kono …ďe ayniraali …óum no haani aynireede. Men okki njo…ďdi gom…óim…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe. Ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ď…ďe ko faasiqii…ďe"
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe! Hulee Allah, gom…óinon Nulaa…óo Makko on; O ye…óay on ge…óe …ói…ói e mbarjaari Makko ndin, O wa…óana on annoora mo ndayginorton, O haforana on. Pellet, Allah ko Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo"
  57,29,"Fii no yim…ďe Defte …ďen anndira wonnde …ďe hattanaa hay huunde e …ďural Allah ngal, e wonnde …ďural ngal ko e juu…óe Allah woni; Himo ye…óa ngal mo O muuyani. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ďural mawngal"